data.description: This ready to move in Townhouse features 3 bedrooms, 3 baths with an open floor plan and very spacious bedrooms! Newer appliances and a washer and dryer are included. Kitchen and bathroom have digital temp faucets so you know how warm or cold the water is. Has a 2-car garage, fenced back yard, and central A/C. Easy access to I25 & I80 both and just minutes to FE Warren AFB! Hurry this property won't last long!! Schedule your private showing today. Seller is offering $2500 allowance for carpet or seller concessions.
